---
import "../styles/global.css";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
---

<Layout title="Sboonny Portfolio | Home">
  <Header />
  <main class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
      Hi, I am Muhammed Mustafa.
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-500">
      A front end Developer who enjoys contributing to open source projects. I
      work mainly with <span class="font-bold text-blue-600">TypeScript</span>
       and <span class="font-bold text-blue-400">React</span>.
    </p>

    <section>
      <h2>About</h2>
      <p>
        I have always wanted to be a programmer, but whatever tools or course I
        used to learn programming, end with my disappointment. Tried to focus on
        business to earn living, but who known that my interaction with business
        will guide me to <a
          class="dark:text-gray-100 text-gray-900 font-bold"
          href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hp1INWuXIgo&pp=ygUaY29mZmVlemlsbGEgZnJlZSBjb2RlIGNhbXA%3D"
          rel="noreferrer noopener"
          target="_blank">freeCodeCamp</a
        >.
      </p>
    </section>
    <div class="relative">
      <span>2022-SEP 2023</span><a
        class="dark:text-gray-100 text-gray-900 font-bold"
        href="https://www.freecodecamp.org/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Frontend Dev - freeCodeCamp</a
      >
      <p>
        I previously worked on freeCodeCamp as a maintainer, my focus was
        clearing the front end tasks there.
      </p>
    </div>
    <section>
      <h2 class="my-12 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        Projects that I worked on with others ü§ù.
      </h2>

      <div class="bg-gray-700 p-5 shadow-lg">
        <a href="" class="rounded-md text-gray-300 shadow-sm dark:text-gray-100"
          ><span class="sr-only">Check</span>Chapter
        </a>

        <p class="text-gray-300">
          I was lucky to have worked in chapter with awesome collages, and
          talented individuals who contributed to that codebase.
        </p>

        <details class="text-purple-200">
          <summary>About</summary>
           Chapter was an attempt to build a meet up platform, that you can
          self-host through a Docker container Docker and deploy to the cloud
          with a one-click and then configured. No coding required.
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-700 p-5 shadow-lg">
        <a href="" class="rounded-md text-gray-300 shadow-sm dark:text-gray-100"
          ><span class="sr-only">Check</span>freeCodeCamp
        </a>

        <p class="text-gray-300">
          I contributed to freeCodeCamp, an open source community that helps you
          learn to code, build projects, and earn certifications.
        </p>

        <details class="text-purple-200">
          <summary>About</summary>
           freeCodeCamp is a non-profit organization that consists of an
          interactive learning web platform, an online community forum, chat
          rooms, Medium publications, and local organizations that intend to
          make learning web development accessible to anyone.
        </details>
      </div>

      <ul>
        <li>Worked on <a href="https://github.com/freeCodeCamp/chapter/pull/2301" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">implementing search function</a> using React `useState` as state management.</li>
        <li>Paired on fixing loading of the data bug in the homepage, and <a href="https://github.com/freeCodeCamp/chapter/pull/2340" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">removed the extra query</a>.</li>
        <li>Worked on making chapter responsive, you can check it by running a <a href="https://gitpod.io/#https://github.com/freeCodeCamp/chapter" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Gitpod</a> instance.</li>
        <li>Worked on <a href="https://github.com/freeCodeCamp/freeCodeCamp/pull/50286" rel="noopener noreferrer">Restful API, and implemented test</a> for it.</li>
        <li>Helped freeCodeCamp issue by implementing <a href="https://github.com/freeCodeCamp/freeCodeCamp/pulls?q=is%3Apr+author%3ASboonny+is%3Aclosed+">small pull requests</a> that solves issue in small steps.</li>
        <li>Helped with rewrite of the old API to a <a href="https://github.com/freeCodeCamp/freeCodeCamp/pulls?q=is%3Apr+label%3A%22platform%3A+api%22+author%3ASboonny+is%3Aclosed" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fastify</a> based one.</li>
      </ul>

    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
